{"article_id":"i0LTG3lZ0Xs94aOm","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Michael Cohen , the man","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"tasked with keeping Donald Trump 's deepest secrets ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"offered Congress a damning portrait of his former boss on Wednesday ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"the president encouraged him to lie to Congress and the public for Trump 's protection .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"During an often combative appearance before a House committee , Cohen delivered a searing account of his dealings with the man","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"who he helped win the White House ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"casting Trump as a `` racist , '' a `` con man '' and a `` cheat ''","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"and tying the White House more directly than ever to criminal investigations","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"that have shadowed Trump 's presidency .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"And","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"when his own credibility was directly and frequently challenged as a recently convicted felon","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"who lied to Congress two years ago about his own dealings on behalf of the president ,","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"Cohen countered","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that he had served Trump and his business for a decade","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"and that few people are in a better position","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"to offer insights about his former boss and the organization","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"he built around himself .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"`` He does n't give orders , ''","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Cohen told the committee .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"`` He speaks in a code .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"And I understand the code ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"because I 've been around him for a decade . ''","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"In more than six hours of sworn testimony , Cohen asserted","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that Trump knew","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"WikiLeaks planned to release stolen emails","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"that were damaging to political rival Hillary Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"`` Would n't that be great , ''","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"he said","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Trump replied","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"when informed of the prospect during the 2016 campaign .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Cohen told the panel","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"that Trump helped engineer and personally reimbursed Cohen for an illegal hush-money payment to a porn star ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"then told him to lie about the arrangement .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"And he said","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"the president indirectly encouraged him to lie to Congress about his pursuit of a potentially lucrative Trump Tower development in Moscow ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"even as Trump repeatedly denied any business interests in Russia throughout the 2016 campaign .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"`` Mr. Trump did not directly tell me to lie to Congress , ''","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"`` That 's not how he operates .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"He would look me in the eye","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"and tell me","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"there 's no business in Russia","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"and then go out","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"and lie to the American people","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"by saying the same thing .","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"In his way he was telling me to lie about it . ''","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Cohen said","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"he shared his false statement with Trump 's personal lawyers ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"including Jay Sekulow ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"before he provided it to Congress .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"`` There were several changes","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"that were made '' during that review ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"The disclosures went on ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"as Cohen suggested","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"that Trump knew in advance of a June 2016 meeting at Trump Tower ,","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"headed by Donald Trump Jr. ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"in which a Russian lawyer promised to provide damaging information on Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"`` I recalled","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"Don Jr. leaning over to his father","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"and speaking in a low voice ,","depth":15},{"id":63,"text":"which I could clearly hear ,","depth":15},{"id":64,"text":"and saying :","depth":15},{"id":65,"text":"'The meeting is all set . '","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"I remember Mr. Trump , saying ,","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"'OK , good ... let me know . ''","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"Cohen , however , could not pinpoint","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"when he saw the interaction between father and son .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"Nor did he elaborate","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"on","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"whether the two could have been referring to another unrelated meeting .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"The series of events","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"described by Cohen ,","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"who is set to begin a three-year prison term","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"for pleading guilty to a string of financial crimes and lying to Congress ,","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"are at the heart of several ongoing criminal investigations ,","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"including Justice Department special counsel Robert Mueller 's inquiry into Russia 's interference in the 2016 election .","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"And he disclosed","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"that he remains in `` constant contact '' with federal prosecutors from Manhattan","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"who are in the midst of a wide-ranging review","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"that includes the Trump Organization .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"Part of that investigation ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Cohen said ,","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"involves his most recent conversation with the president ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"which occurred","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"two months after the FBI raided the attorney 's offices and home in April 2018 .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Cohen said","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"other conduct","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"involving the president","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"also was under investigation by the Manhattan prosecutors .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"He declined to elaborate ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"because he said","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"prosecutors had asked him not to .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"He acknowledged","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"that he hoped","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"his cooperation could lead to a reduced prison term .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Cohen :","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"From Trump fixer to Mueller informant :","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"Timeline of Michael Cohen 's role in Russia probe","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"Highlights :","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"From threatening schools to racist remarks :","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"Five alleged Trump deeds","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Cohen plans to share","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"`` I am ashamed of my weakness and misplaced loyalty","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"- of the things","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"I did for Mr. Trump","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"in an effort","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"to protect and promote him , ''","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"`` I am ashamed","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"that I chose to take part","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"in concealing Mr. Trump 's illicit acts","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"rather than listening to my conscience .","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"I am ashamed","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"because I know what Mr. Trump is .","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"He is a racist .","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"He is a con man .","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"He is a cheat . ''","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"Cohen acknowledged his past criminal conduct","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"his testimony represented a clean break from Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"whose actions Cohen described as akin to those of a Mob boss .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"`` I have done bad things ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"but I am not a bad man .","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"I have fixed things ,","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"but I am no longer your fixer , Mr. Trump , ''","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"Cohen said ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"that he would not seek or accept a pardon","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"should one be offered by the president .","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"In addition to his written testimony , Cohen arrived at the House Oversight and Government Reform Committee hearing Wednesday with documents","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"that appeared to back up some of his claims ,","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"including a $ 35,000 check","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"signed by Trump .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"Cohen said","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"the personal check ,","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"signed during the first year of his presidency ,","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"was one of 11 `` installment '' payments","depth":14},{"id":140,"text":"to reimburse him for the hush money payment to adult film star Stormy Daniels ,","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"who says","depth":16},{"id":142,"text":"she had an affair with Trump .","depth":16},{"id":143,"text":"Other installment checks were signed by Donald Trump Jr. and Trump Organization finance chief Allen Weisselberg ,","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"Asked by Rep. Ro Khanna , D-Calif. ,","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"whether his testimony indicated","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"that they and Trump had engaged in a `` criminal conspiracy of financial fraud , ''","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"Cohen replied :","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"`` Yes . ''","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"Cohen ticked off a list of names of people","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"who could provide additional information about the transactions ,","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"including Weisselberg , Trump Organization attorney Alan Garten and David Pecker , publisher of the National Enquirer ,","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"who assisted in the hush money scheme .","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"Federal prosecutors in New York say","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"Trump ' s private business reimbursed Cohen $ 130,000 for his payment to Daniels ,","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"added another $ 130,000","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"to cover his taxes","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"and paid him a $ 60,000 bonus on top of that ,","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"then disguised the payments as legal bills .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"`` Everything was done with the knowledge and at the direction of Mr. Trump , ''","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"Cohen said","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"Trump orchestrated the `` cover-up ''","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"and directed him to lie about the transactions , even to the president 's wife .","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"`` Lying to the first lady is one of my biggest regrets , ''","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"Cohen said","depth":13},{"id":167,"text":"as camera shutters clicked .","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"`` She is a kind , good person .","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"I respect her greatly ,","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"and she did not deserve that . ''","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"Cohen said","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"Trump 's misconduct extended to the characterization of his personal financial status .","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"`` It was my experience that Mr. Trump inflated his total assets","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"when it served his purposes ,","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"such as trying to be listed among the wealthiest people in Forbes ,","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"and deflated his assets","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"to reduce his real estate taxes , ''","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"Cohen said .","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"Trump also inflated the value of his assets","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"to obtain insurance policies .","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"Trump did n't even wait for Cohen to begin his testimony","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"before firing back from Vietnam ,","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"where he was meeting with North Korean leader Kim Jong Un .","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"`` Michael Cohen was one of many lawyers","depth":14},{"id":186,"text":"who represented me","depth":15},{"id":187,"text":"( unfortunately ) , ''","depth":15},{"id":188,"text":"Trump tweeted from Hanoi , site of his second summit with Kim .","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"`` He had other clients also . ''","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"Noting","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"that Cohen has been disbarred ,","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"the president said","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"`` he did bad things","depth":14},{"id":194,"text":"unrelated to Trump , ''","depth":14},{"id":195,"text":"and `` is lying","depth":14},{"id":196,"text":"in order to reduce his prison time . ''","depth":14},{"id":197,"text":"Cohen 's testimony , however , went beyond Trump 's business and campaign dealings","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"to describe his former boss a `` a racist . ''","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"`` In private , he was even worse , ''","depth":13},{"id":200,"text":"the attorney said .","depth":13},{"id":201,"text":"`` He once asked","depth":14},{"id":202,"text":"if I could name a country","depth":15},{"id":203,"text":"run by a black person","depth":16},{"id":204,"text":"that was n't a 'shithole . ' ...","depth":16},{"id":205,"text":"While we were once driving through a struggling neighborhood in Chicago ,","depth":15},{"id":206,"text":"he commented","depth":16},{"id":207,"text":"that only black people could live that way .","depth":16},{"id":208,"text":"And he told me","depth":16},{"id":209,"text":"that black people would never vote for him","depth":17},{"id":210,"text":"because they were too stupid .","depth":17},{"id":211,"text":"And yet I continued to work for him . ''","depth":15},{"id":212,"text":"The House committee 's chairman , Rep. Elijah Cummings , D-Md. , warned Cohen","depth":11},{"id":213,"text":"that members would seek to assess his credibility","depth":12},{"id":214,"text":"given his criminal conduct , as well as the president 's .","depth":12},{"id":215,"text":"Lawmakers sought details on everything from Trump 's finances to the operation of his private business .","depth":11},{"id":216,"text":"They also questioned","depth":12},{"id":217,"text":"whether Trump complied with tax laws and campaign finance regulations .","depth":12},{"id":218,"text":"Cohen has confessed to committing crimes for Trump 's benefit ,","depth":11},{"id":219,"text":"and he came ready to unload on the president Wednesday .","depth":11},{"id":220,"text":"Trump 's defenders were equally ready for fireworks .","depth":11},{"id":221,"text":"Hours before Cohen was due to testify ,","depth":13},{"id":222,"text":"one of the president 's staunchest defenders in Congress , Rep. Matt Gaetz , R-Fla. , asked him on Twitter","depth":14},{"id":223,"text":"whether his `` wife & father-in-law know about your girlfriends ? ''","depth":14},{"id":224,"text":"He mused :","depth":13},{"id":225,"text":"`` I wonder","depth":15},{"id":226,"text":"if she ' ll remain faithful","depth":16},{"id":227,"text":"when you ' re in prison .","depth":16},{"id":228,"text":"She ' s about to learn a lot . ''","depth":14},{"id":229,"text":"On Wednesday , Republican members sought to postpone the hearing ,","depth":10},{"id":230,"text":"claiming","depth":11},{"id":231,"text":"that Cohen had not provided a copy of his testimony in a timely manner .","depth":11},{"id":232,"text":"The effort was derailed ,","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":"but the fight","depth":12},{"id":234,"text":"to discredit Trump 's former lawyer","depth":12},{"id":235,"text":"went on .","depth":11},{"id":236,"text":"Ohio Rep. Jim Jordan , the panel 's ranking Republican , seized on Cohen 's past false statements to Congress .","depth":14},{"id":237,"text":"`` Here we go , ''","depth":16},{"id":238,"text":"Jordan told the packed gallery .","depth":16},{"id":239,"text":"`` This might be the first time","depth":18},{"id":240,"text":"someone","depth":20},{"id":241,"text":"convicted of lying to Congress","depth":20},{"id":242,"text":"has been brought back ''","depth":19},{"id":243,"text":"to testify so quickly .","depth":17},{"id":244,"text":"`` We are legitimizing dishonesty , ''","depth":18},{"id":245,"text":"Jordan said .","depth":18},{"id":246,"text":"`` We are de-legitimizing this institution . ''","depth":17},{"id":247,"text":"As Cohen read from the 20-page statement ,","depth":15},{"id":248,"text":"Rep. Mark Meadows , R-N.C. , shook his head in visible contempt .","depth":15},{"id":249,"text":"Rep. James Comer , R-Ky. , also drilled Cohen ,","depth":16},{"id":250,"text":"referring to the attorney 's admitted criminal conduct","depth":16},{"id":251,"text":"and then drew a ripple of laughter with a brief question","depth":16},{"id":252,"text":"followed by an unexpected answer .","depth":16},{"id":253,"text":"Virtually every question from a Republican lawmaker contained a reference to Cohen 's damaged credibility .","depth":13},{"id":254,"text":"Few sought more information about Cohen 's claims against Trump .","depth":13},{"id":255,"text":"When it was Rep. Paul Gosar , R-Airz. , turn ,","depth":12},{"id":256,"text":"a poster appeared behind the Republican members","depth":13},{"id":257,"text":"carrying the slogan :","depth":14},{"id":258,"text":"`` Liar Liar Pants on Fire ! ''","depth":14},{"id":259,"text":"At one point , the tense exchanges prompted Rep. Stephen Lynch , D-Mass. , to challenge Republicans :","depth":12},{"id":260,"text":"`` Your side ran away from the truth , ''","depth":14},{"id":261,"text":"Lynch thundered .","depth":14},{"id":262,"text":"`` We 're trying to bring it to the American people . ''","depth":13},{"id":263,"text":"Cohen then interjected ,","depth":13},{"id":264,"text":"urging skeptical Republicans to review the documents","depth":14},{"id":265,"text":"that supported his claims against the president .","depth":14},{"id":266,"text":"`` You do n't have to take my word for it , ''","depth":14},{"id":267,"text":"Cohen said at one point .","depth":14},{"id":268,"text":"`` Look at the documents ...","depth":14},{"id":269,"text":"I did the same thing","depth":16},{"id":270,"text":"that you are doing now .","depth":16},{"id":271,"text":"I protected Mr. Trump for 10 years . ''","depth":15},{"id":272,"text":"Cohen had long been among Trump 's most voluble defenders .","depth":11},{"id":273,"text":"Responding to a question from Rep. Jackie Speier , D-Calif. ,","depth":13},{"id":274,"text":"Cohen said","depth":13},{"id":275,"text":"he threatened as many as 500 people at Trump 's behest ,","depth":13},{"id":276,"text":"including journalists .","depth":13},{"id":277,"text":"But last year ,","depth":13},{"id":278,"text":"before he was sentenced to prison ,","depth":14},{"id":279,"text":"he told a judge","depth":14},{"id":280,"text":"he had been blinded by misguided loyalty .","depth":12},{"id":281,"text":"`` Time and time again , I felt","depth":13},{"id":282,"text":"it was my duty to cover up his dirty deeds , ''","depth":13},{"id":283,"text":"he said at the time .","depth":12},{"id":284,"text":"Cohen , the combative lawyer","depth":12},{"id":285,"text":"who once vowed","depth":13},{"id":286,"text":"that he would `` take a bullet '' for his former boss ,","depth":13},{"id":287,"text":"has pleaded guilty","depth":11},{"id":288,"text":"and agreed to cooperate in investigations of Russian interference in the 2016 election and illegal payments to women","depth":11},{"id":289,"text":"who claimed to have had sex with Trump .","depth":11},{"id":290,"text":"Both Cohen and the Justice Department have alleged in court","depth":11},{"id":291,"text":"that Trump directed Cohen to make the payments ,","depth":11},{"id":292,"text":"though they stopped short of accusing the president himself of violating the law .","depth":10},{"id":293,"text":"Trump has said","depth":11},{"id":294,"text":"he was not involved in Cohen 's crimes","depth":11},{"id":295,"text":"and has described his former lawyer as a `` liar '' and a `` rat . ''","depth":10},{"id":296,"text":"White House spokeswoman Sarah Sanders said","depth":10},{"id":297,"text":"`` it 's laughable that anyone would take a convicted liar like Cohen at his word ,","depth":11},{"id":298,"text":"and pathetic to see him given yet another opportunity","depth":12},{"id":299,"text":"to spread his lies . ''","depth":12},{"id":300,"text":"At the end of more than six hours Wednesday , Cohen appeared spent .","depth":8},{"id":301,"text":"He wiped tears from his eyes","depth":11},{"id":302,"text":"as Cummings offered an emotional postscript to the extraordinary session ,","depth":11},{"id":303,"text":"suggesting","depth":11},{"id":304,"text":"that Cohen 's testimony could help repair a wounded government .","depth":11},{"id":305,"text":"`` I 've sat here","depth":12},{"id":306,"text":"and listened to all of this ,","depth":12},{"id":307,"text":"and it 's very painful ;","depth":12},{"id":308,"text":"it 's very painful , ''","depth":12},{"id":309,"text":"Cummings said .","depth":10},{"id":310,"text":"Cohen 's testimony Wednesday does not end his interaction with Congress .","depth":8},{"id":311,"text":"He is scheduled to testify again in closed session Thursday before the House Intelligence Committee .","depth":8},{"id":312,"text":"Testimony :","depth":5},{"id":313,"text":"Michael Cohen , once keeper of Donald Trump 's secrets , plans to accuse the president of 'criminal conduct '","depth":5},{"id":314,"text":"Takeaways :","depth":5},{"id":315,"text":"Cohen takeaways :","depth":6},{"id":316,"text":"As Trump 's former lawyer heads to prison ,","depth":7},{"id":317,"text":"political and legal implications grow for White House","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":635,"left":0,"right":634,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":634,"left":414,"right":633,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":414,"left":389,"right":413,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":389,"left":322,"right":388,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":322,"left":320,"right":321,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":320,"left":319,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":319,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":321,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":388,"left":339,"right":387,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":339,"left":326,"right":338,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":326,"left":323,"right":325,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":323,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":325,"left":8,"right":324,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":324,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":338,"left":333,"right":337,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":333,"left":329,"right":332,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":329,"left":328,"right":14,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":328,"left":11,"right":327,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":327,"left":12,"right":1